Title: To The Test: Concentrated Sophic Vellum
Description:
The Order and shadowflame magics are competing with each other. The enchantment will never be able to funnel Fyr'alath's power if we can't channel the excess Order magic being forced away from it.

If you can channel the enchantment, your allies can catch any excess Order magic.
ObjectivesText: Return the excess Order magic to Shalasar's Sophic Vellum.

Objectives.Text: Order magic returned to Shalasar's Sophic Vellum.
